      <div class="SOTTO_PARA">
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e9268"> </a>Position the light support (1) on the steering tube and fasten it by starting the screws (2).
         </div>
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e9270"> </a>Tighten the screws (3) to a torque of 25 Nm ±10%.
         </div>
