         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e9275"> </a>Lay out wiring front section on headlight support (1) and fit cable rings.
         </div>
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e9277"> </a>Fasten wiring using ties (A).
         </div>
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e9279"> </a>Apply the recommended threadlocker to the screws (2).
         </div>
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e9281"> </a>Tighten the two screws (2) to a torque of 1.5 Nm ±10%.
         </div>
      </div>
      <div class="AggancioFigure">
         <center><img class="Default" src="img/DUC_MO_MTS1200_7_035603519.jpg"></center>
