         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e9286"> </a>Position the headlight assembly (5) on headlight support (1).
         </div>
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e9288"> </a>If the screws (4) are not new, smear them with specified threadlocker.
         </div>
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e9290"> </a>Start and tighten the screws (4) to a torque of 5 Nm ± 10%.
         </div>
      </div>
